{"tid":143403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【信我冇死】 大家記得寫日記，人生最寶貴係回憶","createTime":"2017-03-04T14:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T07:56:04.000Z","uid":61443,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1079e158755ffb2b4d8ad3fe4f053c3bb739372","tid":143403,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:46:07.000Z","msg":"頭先執屋<br />\n櫃底有本簿仔<br />\n一打開原來係1x年前既日記 (自己都唔撚記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n果陣寫低左中學發生既事 <br />\n睇返啲字跡同文筆笑到仆街 <br />\n咁我果陣呢<br />\n會寫低發生咩事同埋個心情係點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n原來我記低左<br />\n自己同老死點樣嘈交 <br />\n仲小氣到寫住呢世冇識到呢個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n ~~而家我就黎做佢伴郎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />~~<br />\n<br />\n中意左隔離班個女仔 <br />\n點樣大膽識佢 <br />\n果陣仲係日記寫左軍令狀<br />\n果日識唔到佢就死鬼左佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後果日識唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n~~唔記得散左幾多年嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ~~ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1x年後睇返會心微笑 <br />\n原來果陣死去活來既嘢<br />\n今日都係碎料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇返以前自己呢種感覺好好 <br />\n大家記得寫日記吖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8457e9b7058a124f53b377a76996f06c0ca3d2","tid":143403,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/zJI_Hn0G16Q/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FzJI_Hn0G16Q%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=f7138c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實最寶貴既嘢<br />\n一直都係自己到<br />\n係大家有冇好好去保管佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68431d44980006872035a5816fa8d08537a5ce1b","tid":143403,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1f2bb27057f627d286c21545e936aec8eb20236","tid":143403,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>回憶真係好寶貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我唔想要</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無論好同壞<br />\n係令你成長必經路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9748470bde6202aef1089c9b8e4d32850e4e623c","tid":143403,"uid":39049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:56:45.000Z","msg":"我都寫左差唔多十四年, 五千幾篇, 以前日記板係全公開, d fd 上黎留言, 熱鬧過chatroom"},{"pid":"3ca1226329fccb597b28cfdf7bd26e29771fb269","tid":143403,"uid":33040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5e8bf1a29770a4af58101c23865dd04677f567","tid":143403,"uid":57584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:05:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c62d29464138165bf7eb7bd8310f0aa08608b066","tid":143403,"uid":67837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"睇返以前既日記都覺得好開心 單靠記憶真係會唔記得好多野"}]}